<div class="bodyCopy">
	
	<h2>Getting connected to Internode ADSL2+ broadband is easy!<img style="float: right;" src="/media/images/products/easy-abc-blocks.jpg" alt="Internode Easy Home Broadband" width="200" height="180"></h2>
<p>Choose from:</p>
<ul>
<li><a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/easy_broadband/"><strong>Easy Broadband</strong></a> - Super-fast ADSL2+ speeds direct from the Internode broadband access network. A range of monthly quotas, all the way from 50 GB to 1.2 Terabytes!</li>
<li style="margin-top: 9px;"><a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/easy_naked/"><strong>Easy Naked</strong></a> - Super-fast ADSL2+ speeds with no phone line rental required.</li>
<li style="margin-top: 9px;"><a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/easy_reach/"><strong>Easy Reach</strong></a> - Australia-wide ADSL2+ where Easy Broadband isn't available.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<div class="BoxGeneric">
<p style="text-align: center;">Not sure what to choose? <strong><a href="/coverage">See what's available in your area</a></strong>.</p>
</div>
<h2>More than a bundle...</h2>
<p>Your complete combo package of ADSL, home phone, mobile SIM and Fetch TV.</p>
<p><a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/easy_broadband/combos/"><strong>Read more about our three great value Combos</strong></a></p>
<h2>The Roadmap&hellip;</h2>
<p>Confused about all the ADSL choices and options? We've created this roadmap 'cheat sheet' to help you decide which one is right for you:</p>
<p><a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/roadmap/"><strong>Learn more about Internode ADSL</strong></a></p>
<h2>Need a Broadband router or other equipment?</h2>
<p>To ensure you're using your Internode ADSL service to its full potential, you need to use the most effective hardware to connect to the Internet.</p>
<p><a href="/residential/adsl_broadband/hardware/"><strong>Choose from our great range of ADSL Broadband hardware</strong></a></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>	
